        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Fairness in Nursing Home Arbitration Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits, and nullifies any existing, pre-dispute arbitration agreements with respect to Medicare skilled nursing facilities or Medicaid nursing facilities, home- and community-based services, or home health care services.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
